I'm so happy. Then I'll be waiting for you, so look forward to it, okay？

I see... It was so sudden, so you don't have to worry. See you next time.

Yes, and I'm a little nervous.
Go ahead and relax for a bit.

I really like to have matching tableware with you.

I think it was normal, don't you think？
Really！？ I thought it was a failure...
